<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="student-page">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Anti-Ragging Portal
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
            <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white py-4">
              <h2 class="mb-0">
                <i class="fas fa-gavel me-2"></i>Anti-Ragging Penalties &
                Punishments
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <div class="alert alert-danger mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                <strong>Zero Tolerance Policy:</strong> Our institution has a
                strict zero-tolerance policy towards ragging.
              </div>

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-3">Legal Provisions</h4>
              <p>
                Ragging is a criminal offense under Indian law. The following
                acts govern anti-ragging measures:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>UGC Regulations 2009:</strong> Prevention and
                  Prohibition of Ragging in Higher Educational Institutions
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Supreme Court Directive:</strong> Mandatory compliance
                  with anti-ragging measures
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>IPC Sections:</strong> Various sections applicable
                  based on severity of offense
                </li>
              </ul>

              <hr class="my-4" />

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-3">
                Punishments at Institution Level
              </h4>

              <div class="accordion" id="punishmentAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#minor"
                    >
                      <i
                        class="fas fa-exclamation-circle text-warning me-2"
                      ></i>
                      <strong>For Minor Offenses</strong>
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="minor"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    data-bs-parent="#punishmentAccordion"
                  >
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <ul>
                        <li>Written apology to the victim</li>
                        <li>Community service</li>
                        <li>Suspension from classes for specific period</li>
                        <li>Withholding scholarship/fellowship</li>
                        <li>Debarring from representing institution</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#major"
                    >
                      <i
                        class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-danger me-2"
                      ></i>
                      <strong>For Major Offenses</strong>
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="major"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    data-bs-parent="#punishmentAccordion"
                  >
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <ul>
                        <li>
                          Suspension from the institution for specific period
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          Rustication from the institution for one or more
                          semesters
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          Expulsion from the institution and debarring from
                          admission to any other institution
                        </li>
                        <li>Cancellation of admission</li>
                        <li>Withholding results</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                  <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button
                      class="accordion-button collapsed"
                      type="button"
                      data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                      data-bs-target="#criminal"
                    >
                      <i class="fas fa-handcuffs text-dark me-2"></i>
                      <strong>Criminal Proceedings</strong>
                    </button>
                  </h2>
                  <div
                    id="criminal"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    data-bs-parent="#punishmentAccordion"
                  >
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <ul>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Imprisonment:</strong> Up to 3 years for
                          severe cases
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Fine:</strong> Up to â‚¹25,000 or as per court
                          decision
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>Criminal Record:</strong> Permanent criminal
                          record affecting future prospects
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <strong>FIR Filing:</strong> Mandatory filing of FIR
                          in serious cases
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <hr class="my-4" />

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-danger mb-3">
                What Constitutes Ragging?
              </h4>
              <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="fw-bold">Physical Ragging:</h6>
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Assault, physical harm</li>
                        <li>Forced physical exercises</li>
                        <li>Stripping or forcing obscene acts</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="fw-bold">Verbal/Mental Ragging:</h6>
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Teasing, abusing, threatening</li>
                        <li>Asking to do menial tasks</li>
                        <li>Psychological pressure</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="fw-bold">Cyber Ragging:</h6>
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Online harassment</li>
                        <li>Sharing morphed images</li>
                        <li>Bullying on social media</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="fw-bold">Sexual Harassment:</h6>
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Any form of sexual abuse</li>
                        <li>Obscene gestures/comments</li>
                        <li>Inappropriate touching</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="alert alert-warning mt-4">
                <h6 class="fw-bold">
                  <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>Remember:
                </h6>
                <ul class="mb-0 small">
                  <li>Ragging is NOT a tradition - it's a CRIME</li>
                  <li>Silence is NOT an option - REPORT immediately</li>
                  <li>
                    You are protected - your identity will be kept confidential
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    No student shall be allowed to graduate if found guilty of
                    ragging
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/complaint/submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg">
                  <i class="fas fa-file-alt me-2"></i>Report a Ragging Incident
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white py-3 mt-5">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2024 Anti-Ragging Portal</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
